data.description: Discover the allure of this enchanting tree-lined neighborhood nestled in the highly sought-after Pines at Dickinson community, conveniently situated in the village of Kings Contrivance. This wonderful garden condo boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths and has been recently upgraded. Bask in the welcoming ambiance of the spacious living room, adorned with abundant natural light and a captivating fireplace.  The newly renovated kitchen exudes modern charm with pristine white shaker cabinetry and new appliances. Enhancing the kitchen's appeal is a convenient passthrough, offering space for two bar stools or simply opening up your view to the living area. This open layout is ideal for keeping the chef company or enjoying a quick, casual meal on the go. Step through the sliding doors from the living room to access your private patio, where you can unwind in the park-like surroundings on warm summer evenings or savor your favorite beverage in the morning.  The three generously sized bedrooms provide ample space, while the hall's full bath boasts a new vanity, and the primary bathroom features a new vanity and updated tile. Abundant storage space adds to the condo's practicality. Revel in the ample parking and the proximity to Harris Teeter, Starbucks, and Dickinson Park. Enjoy quick access to shopping, restaurants, and extensive outdoor recreation, including over 100 miles of paved trails spanning the Villages of Columbia, the three Columbia Lakes, and the renowned Merriweather Post Pavilion for concerts and festivals.  Benefit from easy commuting routes to Baltimore, DC, Annapolis, Frederick, and surrounding areas. This prime Columbia/Howard County location is just minutes away from Ft Meade, NSA, BWI, and commuter rail stations. Immerse yourself in the epitome of convenience and comfort in this desirable community.
